Security Threats and Risks for Open
Pluggable Edge Services (OPES)
2004", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC3837.html", target="_top", tooltip="The document investigates the security threats associated with the Open Pluggable Edge Services (OPES) and discusses the effects of security threats on the underlying architecture.  The main goal of this document is threat discovery and analysis.  The document does not specify or recommend any solutions.  This memo provides information for the Internet community."];
