Open Pluggable Edge Services (OPES)
Treatment of IAB Considerations
2004", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC3914.html", target="_top", tooltip="IETF Internet Architecture Board (IAB) expressed nine architecture-level considerations for the Open Pluggable Edge Services (OPES) framework.  This document describes how OPES addresses those considerations.  This memo provides information for the Internet community."];
